Description: Cylinder seal of black steatite: slightly worn at the ends and perforated through the centre. The seal is inscribed with an incised text. Good condition.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit II (Wiesbaden, 1964), 1164; P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit III (Wiesbaden, 1964), pl. 109, abb. 558.
